  Sounds like the same problem JP had on the way to Colorado. After changing
every removable part the bus would still run the same. Finally changed out
the dizzy with the petronix in it and bus ran like a champ after that. After
all the work it turned out the electronic ignition had started to take a
dump. So try a new dizzy with points and see if it makes a difference.

ronnie

